INSERT INTO items VALUES(2270,268,39,'PROC','MOT 20-072','PROC_VILLAGE_RULES PROC_VILLAGE_POLICY PUB_ENG_MEET The first choice, "PROC_VILLAGE_RULES," was made because the agenda item involves the approval of minutes from previous village board meetings. This process is a standard procedure that ensures that the records of meetings are formally recognized and maintained according to the rules and regulations governing the village''s official proceedings. The action of approving minutes is closely aligned with procedural rules related to how meetings are conducted, documented, and validated in a municipal governance context.','A. MOT 20-072 Motion to Approve Minutes from Regular Remote Meeting of October 19, 2020 and Special Remote Meeting of October 26, 2020 of the Village Board.','d0fa8767-7e7b-45f0-b91f-bcedff1d439b',189,'2024-10-28T01:59:45','2024-11-05T04:38:59',replace('A. MOT 20-072 Motion to Approve Minutes from Regular Remote Meeting of October 19,\n2020 and Special Remote Meeting of October 26, 2020 of the Village Board.\nIt was moved by Village Trustee Boutet and seconded by Village Trustee\nMoroney to approve the minutes from October 19, 2020 and October 26, 2020 as\npresented. A roll call vote was taken. The motion was approved. The roll call\nvote was as follows:\nAYES: 6 - Village President Abu-Taleb, Village Trustee Andrews, Village Trustee Boutet,\nVillage Trustee Buchanan, Village Trustee Moroney, and Village Trustee Taglia\nNAYS: 0\nABSENT: 1 - Village Trustee Walker-Peddakotla\n','\n',char(10)),NULL);
