INSERT INTO items VALUES(2287,180,21,'PROC','MOT 24-169','PROC_VILLAGE_RULES PROC_BOARD_RULES PROC_VILLAGE_POLICY The first classification choice is "PROC_VILLAGE_RULES." This agenda item involves a motion to approve minutes from a previous special meeting of the village board. Approving meeting minutes is a procedural task that falls under the general governance and rules associated with conducting village or municipal meetings. Therefore, "PROC_VILLAGE_RULES" is the most relevant category as it focuses on the regulatory aspects of village meetings and procedures.','A. MOT 24-169 A Motion to Approve Minutes from the April 30, 2024 Special Meeting of the Village Board','6be03969-98f2-4c94-b7a0-8e669f93ef46',190,'2024-10-28T01:59:45','2024-11-05T04:39:00',replace('A. MOT 24-169 A Motion to Approve Minutes from the April 30, 2024 Special Meeting of\nthe Village Board\nIt was moved by Trustee Robinson, seconded by Trustee Wesley, to approve the\nMinutes. A voice vote was taken and the motion was approved.\n','\n',char(10)),1);
