e Taglia, Village Trustee Tucker, and Village\nTrustee Boutet\nNAYS: 3 - Village President Abu-Taleb, Village Trustee Moroney, and Village Trustee Andrews\nABSENT: 0\n','\n',char(10)),NULL);
