illage Trustee Taglia, Village President Abu-Taleb, Village Trustee Tucker, Village\nTrustee Moroney, and Village Trustee Andrews\nNAYS: 1 - Village Trustee Boutet\nABSENT: 1 - Village Trustee Button\n','\n',char(10)),NULL);
