INSERT INTO items VALUES(3821,471,422,'PUB_ENG_PROC','MOT 23-41','PUB_ENG_PROC ENV_SUS_CLIM ENV_SUS_PLST The first choice, PUB_ENG_PROC, is chosen because the agenda item involves a proclamation to declare May as "Monarch Butterfly Month," which aligns with public proclamations celebrating community awareness and promoting the importance of biodiversity and environmental conservation. This category encompasses initiatives that raise public awareness and engage the community in environmental causes.','B. MOT 23-41 A Motion to Approve a Proclamation to Declare May as Monarch Butterfly Month','2269586b-5320-42ae-a347-0586304b78e0',319,'2024-10-28T01:59:45','2024-11-05T04:39:00',replace('B. MOT 23-41 A Motion to Approve a Proclamation to Declare May as Monarch Butterfly\nMonth\nTrustee Robinson read the Proclamation into the Record.\nChief Sustainability Officer Marcella Bondie Keenan introduced a video of\nthe butterfly garden at the Public Works Center.\nOak Park Public Library Latinx Language & Culture Librarian Nora\nSanchez presented a butterfly display and connections between monarchs\nand Mexican culture.\nIt was moved by Trustee Parakkat, seconded by Trustee Straw, that this Motion\nbe approved. A voice vote was taken and the motion was approved.\n','\n',char(10)),1);
INSERT INTO items VALUES(3822,893,167,'PUB_ENG_PROC','MOT 23-50','PUB_ENG_PROC ENV_SUS_CLIM PUB_ENG_HEAR The first choice, PUB_ENG_PROC (Proclamations celebrating diversity, community involvement, and public awareness events), fits best because the agenda item revolves around a proclamation. Specifically, this agenda item pertains to declaring May 2023 as National Bike Month, which aligns with promoting community awareness and public engagement through proclamations. This choice reflects a focus on community involvement and public awareness, as noted in the description of PUB_ENG_PROC.','C. MOT 23-50 A Motion to Approve a Proclamation for Proclaiming May 2023 as National Bike Month.','334f8ee2-a207-433d-aac8-331e1e23adbf',319,'2024-10-28T01:59:45','2024-11-05T04:39:00',replace('C. MOT 23-50 A Motion to Approve a Proclamation for Proclaiming May 2023 as National\nBike Month.\nTrustee Buchanan read the Proclamation into the Record.\nIt was moved by Trustee Straw, seconded by Trustee Parakkat, that this Motion\nbe approved. A voice vote was taken and the motion was approved.\n','\n',char(10)),1);
