INSERT INTO items VALUES(4035,6451,65,'TRANS_INF_EXP','RES 18-1017','TRANS_INF_EXP TRANS_INF_TRAFFIC PUB_WRK_ROADS The first classification, TRANS_INF_EXP, was chosen because the agenda item refers to a street-specific project, involving a formal agreement for federal participation in the construction of the Lake Street Streetscape Project. The usage of "construction" and "streetscape" implies a focus on infrastructure improvements that impact traffic, which aligns closely with an expressway project or broader transportation infrastructure enhancement. Additionally, since it specifically involves formal agreements and government participation, it corresponds well with the complexities of projects eligible under envisaged infrastructure expansion initiatives.','W. RES 18-1017 A Resolution Approving A Local Public Agency Agreement For Federal Participation with the State Of Illinois for Construction of the Lake Street Streetscape Project, Section 16-00264-00-PV, and Authorizing Its Execution','48d2cc6a-9e38-40b1-8216-c5af04002472',335,'2024-10-28T01:59:45','2024-10-28T01:59:45',NULL,NULL);
